      "comment": "VILLAIN OF MAGIC (8) ran good time (30.92) when third last start over 531m at Gawler, the second placing in a row. This looks easier and expected to bounce back. BLACK CHIP (1) was fast into stride from box eight to score two back (30.87) then jumped from the same draw last time but got further back when 4th at this track (31.18). Key runner on best form. ALL THE SASS (4) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 2nd over 530m at this track beaten 5.5 lengths (31.40) behind Jalapeno Gem in a Invitation on July 16. Well placed and gets his chance. RANDOM SASS (2) is one of the chances after collecting a minor prize last time.",
